  (7) Dictionary Information Display

     1) At Dictionary Addition 1), either input "6" or move the reverse video
        portion to Dictionary Information and press the Return key. 
        --> This command displays information about the fixed dictionaries and
            dictionaries in which words can be registered which are used for 
            Kana-Kanji conversion.
     < Figure 2.3.18 >





















     The following key operations are possible:

     Keysym  (Command)| Function
     -----------------+----------------------------------------------------
     Up            ^P | Display the previous dictionary    			
     Down          ^N | Display the next dictionary
     Left          ^B | Scroll left
     Right         ^F | Scroll right
                   ^A | Display the beginning of the dictionary information
                   ^E | Display the end of the dictionary information
 	           ^D | Delete this dictionary
 	           ^U | Toggle the in-use state of this dictionary
                      | (The dictionary remains in the server).
     -----------------+----------------------------------------------------

     Press the Meta+Down key to return to the conditions prior to dictionary
     operation.

